<section class="quote bg-light py-5">
	<div class="container py-md-3" data-aos="fade-up">
		<h4>Come to us shell or Buy vagitables, see Suggestions,I don't know how but you will get more profit.</h4>
		<div class="clearfix"></div>
	</div>
</section>

<div class="container-fluid">
    <table class="table">
        <tr class="text-center thead-dark" data-aos="flip-up">
            <th >ITEMNAME</th>
